OL,3,CYoung Muslims collect hundreds of bags
OL,4,Cof litter in New Year's Day street
OL,5,Cclean
OL,7,FThousands of volunteers have gathered
OL,8,Fin towns and cities across the UK for
OL,9,Fan annual street clean on New Year's
OL,10,FDay.
OL,12,FOrganised by the Ahmadiyya Muslim
OL,13,FYouth Association (AMYA) volunteers
OL,14,Fwere up early for morning prayers,
OL,15,Fbefore heading to their local street
OL,16,Fto pick up litter.
OL,18,FPeople from all communities joined in
OL,19,Fthe efforts in Bordon in Hampshire,
OL,20,Fand Crawley in West Sussex as well as
OL,21,Fother places across the country.
