OL,3,CYoung Muslims collect hundreds of bags
OL,4,Cof litter in New Year's Day street
OL,5,Cclean
OL,7,FThe annual event started in 1995, and
OL,8,Fthis year nearly 3,000 volunteers took
OL,9,Fpart.
OL,11,FMore than 600 bags of litter was
OL,12,Fcollected in a single morning, making
OL,13,Fit one of the country's largest faith-
OL,14,Fled environmental initiatives of the
OL,15,FNew Year.
OL,17,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, organiser
OL,18,FAdeel Shah said: "We were joined by
OL,19,Flocal residents, community members and
OL,20,Fcollected bin bags full of litter.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
