OL,7,F"Then we had a warm breakfast at
OL,8,Faround 8 o'clock all across the UK,
OL,9,Fand that's how we started our New
OL,10,FYear's Day by contributing to the
OL,11,Fcommunities that we live in."
OL,13,FThis year's initiative marks thirty
OL,14,Fyears of the Ahmadiyya Muslim Youth
OL,15,FAssociation's New Year Street Clean-
OL,16,Fup, with Friday's event the largest to
OL,17,Fdate.
OL,19,FThe annual clean-up is deeply rooted
OL,20,Fin Islamic teachings that emphasise
OL,21,Fcleanliness and serving one's nation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
