OL,5,Cclean
OL,7,FThese young Muslims were keen to give
OL,8,Fup their new year's morning to help
OL,9,Fout in their local communities.
OL,11,FFarhad Ahmad, the National President
OL,12,Fof AMYA UK, said: "For many years, the
OL,13,FAhmadiyya Muslim Youth Association has
OL,14,Fbeen running projects like this to
OL,15,Fserve the communities and country we
OL,16,Fare so proud to call home!
OL,18,F"At a time when some have incorrectly
OL,19,Fclaimed that Islam is at odds with
OL,20,FBritish values, initiatives like these
OL,21,Fclearly show the opposite.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
