OL,3,CYoung Muslims collect hundreds of bags
OL,4,Cof litter in New Year's Day street
OL,5,Cclean
OL,7,F"In the last two years alone, our
OL,8,Fvolunteers have contributed over
OL,9,F60,000 hours of service across the UK.
OL,10,FWe have raised over #84 million for
OL,11,FBritish charities and have helped to
OL,12,Fprovide more than four million meals
OL,13,Fto those in need.
OL,15,F"We continue to do this because this
OL,16,Fis what our religion teaches us!"
OL,18,FImam Ehtesham Arif, 24, is one of the
OL,19,Fyoungest Imams in the whole country,
OL,20,Fand took part this morning.
