OL,5,Cclean
OL,7,F"Over the past 30 years, tens of
OL,8,Fthousands of volunteers have
OL,9,Fcollectively dedicated roughly thirty
OL,10,Fthousand hours to keeping our streets
OL,11,Fclean," he said.
OL,13,F"I am now 24 years old and can vividly
OL,14,Fremember taking part in these clean-
OL,15,Fups from the age of five!
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
