OL,3,CYoung Muslims collect hundreds of bags
OL,4,Cof litter in New Year's Day street
OL,5,Cclean
OL,7,F"What continues to inspire me is
OL,8,Fseeing children as young as seven
OL,9,Fwaking up as early as six in the
OL,10,Fmorning on new year's day to pray at
OL,11,Fthe mosque and then take part in these
OL,12,Fclean-ups across the country.
OL,14,F"These young people celebrate the new
OL,15,Fyear by first praying to God, and then
OL,16,Fcollectively serving His people. It is
OL,17,Fall part of our faith."
